<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blogist</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wdth,wght@0,75..100,300..800;1,75..100,300..800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link href="css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2991/2991100.png">
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <div id="home">
        <img
          src="img-svg/home-outline.svg"
          width="25px"
          height="25px"
          alt="home icon"
        /><span> Home </span><button>Home</button>
      </div>
      <div id="left--side--button">
        <%if(locals.isLoggedIn) {%>
        <div id="account--setting">
          <button style="cursor: pointer">Setting</button>
        </div>
        <script>
          document.getElementById("account--setting").onclick = function () {
              window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000/profile';
          }
        </script>
          <%} else {%>
        <div id="login--button"><a>Log in</a><button>Log in</button></div>
        <div id="singup--button">
          <button>Sign up</button>
        </div>
        <%}%>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <header>
      <h1>
        <% if(locals.isLoggedIn) {%>
        <span style="background-color: #26e389; padding:10px">Welcome <%=loginUserName%></span><br><br>
        <%}%>
        Write
        <div class="dot"></div>
        Share
        <div class="dot"></div>
        Inspire <br />A blogging platform for <br />
        everyone—no limits, <br />
        <span id="text--in--header">no boundaries</span>
      </h1>
    </header>
    <article id="features--box">
      <div id="privacy--in--box">
        <img
          src="img-svg/shield-half-outline.svg"
          alt="shield represent privacy"
          width="69px"
        />
        <h3>Privacy First Approach</h3>
        <p>
          Your voice matters, and so does your privacy.<br />
          We protect your data at all costs so you can be at ease.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="money--in--box">
        <img
          src="img-svg/cash-outline.svg"
          alt="money represent income"
          width="69px"
        />
        <h3>Earn While You Share</h3>
        <p>
          Your words have value, and so does your time.<br />
          We help you earn from your content while you create.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article id="user--comment">
      <div id="user--comment-info">
        <img
          src="img-svg/uifaces-popular-image.jpg"
          alt="a person"
          width="250px"
          height="250px"
        />
        <h2>Luca Bianchi</h2>
      </div>
      <div id="user--comment-text">
        <h3>
          Luca Bianchi’s Experience with
          <span id="user--comment-text--blogist">Blogist</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          _"I’ve always wanted to share my thoughts and experiences with a wider
          audience,<br />
          but I didn’t want to compromise my privacy. That’s when I found
          Blogist<br />
          The best part? They truly value my data and privacy, making it easy
          to<br />
          feel safe while posting freely.<br />
          Not only do they protect my information, but they also offer the
          chance to<br />
          monetize my content. It’s incredible to earn while doing something I
          love. The<br />
          platform is super easy to use, and I’ve connected with like-minded
          people<br />
          globally. If you're looking to share your voice, this is the place to
          be!"_<br />
          — Luca Bianchi
        </p>
      </div>
      <div id="woman--heart">
        <img
          src="img-svg/undraw_love-it_8pc0.png"
          alt="woman holding a heart"
          width="554px"
          height="938px"
        />
      </div>
      <div id="view--blog--button">
        <button>View blogs</button>
      </div>
    </article>
    <footer>
      <div id="faqs-wrapper">
        <div id="faqs">
          <h2>FAQs :</h2>
          <p>
            <span class="question"
              >Q1: How do I start blogging on Blogist?<br /><br
            /></span>
            A1: <%if(!locals.isLoggedIn) {%>Simply <a href="http://localhost:3000/signup" class="link">sign up</a> for an account,<%}%>
            create your profile, and start writing!<br />
            Once you're ready, hit "Publish" to share your content with the
            world.<br /><br /><br />

            <span class="question"
              >Q2: Is my data safe on Blogist?<br /><br /><br
            /></span>
            A2: Yes! We take your privacy seriously. We protect your data at all
            costs,<br />
            ensuring you can blog without worry.<br /><br /><br />

            <span class="question"
              >Q3: How can I earn money from my blog?<br /><br /><br
            /></span>
            A3: You can monetize your content through ads, sponsored posts, and
            other<br />
            opportunities we offer.<br /><br /><br />

            <span class="question"
              >Q4: Is there a limit to how many posts I can publish?<br /><br /><br
            /></span>
            A4: No limits at all! Feel free to share as many posts as you like.
            We<br />
            believe in giving you full freedom to express yourself.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="copyright">© .... Blogist. All rights reserved.</div>
    </footer>
    <script>
      const loginButton = document.getElementById("login--button");
      if (loginButton) {
        loginButton.onclick = function () {
          window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000/login';
        };
      }

      const signupButton = document.getElementById("singup--button");
      if (signupButton) {
        signupButton.onclick = function () {
          window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000/signup';
        };
      }

      document.getElementById('home').onclick = function() {
        window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000';
      };

      document.querySelector("#view--blog--button button").addEventListener('click', function () {
        window.location.href = 'http://localhost:3000/blogs';
      });

    </script>
  </body>
</html>
